sentences.sentence: The tibialis anterior muscle and deep fascia flaps possess regular vasa vasorum and abundant vascularity.
sentences.translation: 胫骨前肌肌筋膜瓣解剖血管恒定，血运丰富。

sentences.sentence: 244 I/T curves of 111 cases including musculus tibialis anterior, musculus fibularis longus, musculus extensor hallucis longus were measured.
sentences.translation: 测定111例患者胫前肌、腓骨长肌、拇长伸肌的强度时间曲线共244条。

sentences.sentence: The tibialis anterior of the back leg dorsiflexes the ankle, drawing it towards the shin.
sentences.translation: 后腿的胫骨前使脚踝关节背曲，把它向胫骨的方向提。
